title: 820-3435 - turn on, fan max, but no post
message:
Do you get CPU core voltage?
PLT_RESET_L comes on?

"SHP_INTRUDER_L - 1.65v"
Supposing you mean PCH_INTRUDER_L, this denotes a problem with PCH.
You can try to heat it, using quality flux.

title: 820-3435 - turn on, fan max, but no post
message:
CPU - 1.65v
PLT_RESET_L - 3.3v

Yes, it was PCH_INTRUDER_L =D

I tried to warm it up, but it worked.
